    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/a386c9f35c169532a2db87679c74e4e6.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>化身猫咪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我是猫咪》是一款以猫咪为主角的沙盒冒险游戏。打翻花瓶、磨爪家具、偷吃美食、探索禁地...释放天性，做最调皮的喵星人！😼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/ec18f86838ee54d871490c6c797a7a39.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/ec18f86838ee54d871490c6c797a7a39.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/ec18f86838ee54d871490c6c797a7a39.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沙盒探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畅游神秘大世界，每个角落都是你的私人游乐场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/b048512868223b7d41bccf0505db7005.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/b048512868223b7d41bccf0505db7005.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/b048512868223b7d41bccf0505db7005.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>猫咪日常体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑跳扑抓，用爪子&quot;收集&quot;物品，探索每个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偷偷&quot;借&quot;走家里的物品，或是讨好奶奶？全凭你的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/4e9e4aa65bfb12a40e3e3adc2f3cff77.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/4e9e4aa65bfb12a40e3e3adc2f3cff77.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/4e9e4aa65bfb12a40e3e3adc2f3cff77.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>趣味猫咪挑战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解谜题，发掘隐藏在各处的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专属猫咪任务，考验你的机智与身手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/10867685e1a434600f2c6a467e9d4ce3.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/10867685e1a434600f2c6a467e9d4ce3.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/10867685e1a434600f2c6a467e9d4ce3.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>趣味小游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >足球、篮球、抓老鼠...多种趣味小游戏等你来玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/7e2f18f6f9723ac29793cee18bbfa1c1.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/7e2f18f6f9723ac29793cee18bbfa1c1.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/7e2f18f6f9723ac29793cee18bbfa1c1.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大闹一场</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨爪家具、打翻花瓶、乱扔书本...逼真物理效果，让两脚兽们暴跳如雷吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/47e9c3dad719404ea3180130a8490618.poster.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/47e9c3dad719404ea3180130a8490618.webm?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/47e9c3dad719404ea3180130a8490618.mp4?t=1745928304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016840/extras/35a8174024ae58941aeae4366ac1561f.avif?t=1745928304\" width=640 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💥游戏特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 精致沙盒世界，万物皆可互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 随心所欲搞破坏，释放猫咪天性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 完成专属猫咪的趣味任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 多种皮肤配饰，打造个性爱猫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ 挑战人类底线，看看你能调皮到什么程度？</p>",
